<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using Zend_Rest client with a single parameter the server incorrectly responds with An unknown error occured. Please try again.</p>

<p>Reproducible code is</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
class ExampleService
    {

    /**
     * Say Hello
     *
     * @param string $who
     * @return string
     */
    function sayHello($who)
        {
        return "Hello $who, Good Day";
        }
    }

$client = new Zend_Rest_Client('<a href="http://localhost/web/example">http://localhost/web/example</a>');
$client-&gt;sayHello('Davey')-&gt;get();
</code></pre>

